  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hero's Party R is an SRPG developed by NAGINATA SOFT, and published by OTAKU Plan. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/9ecc798a0e332711d9577a405d7091f1.avif?t=1772420076\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Find 30 people to come to the Demon Castle party!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the king received a letter from the demon king, the old enemy of mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although it was obviously a trap, the king decided to take advantage of this opportunity to suppress the Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chosen commander is the newcomer Rutherford.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rutherford accepted the king's entrustment and embarked on the journey of looking for 30 companions with different personalities to attack the Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/4079bc3aeba1b8517687cd28a6dce10a.avif?t=1772420076\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Japanese SRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 characters to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich story</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hero's Party R is an SRPG developed by NAGINATA SOFT, and published by OTAKU Plan. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/9ecc798a0e332711d9577a405d7091f1.avif?t=1772420076\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Find 30 people to come to the Demon Castle party!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the king received a letter from the demon king, the old enemy of mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although it was obviously a trap, the king decided to take advantage of this opportunity to suppress the Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chosen commander is the newcomer Rutherford.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rutherford accepted the king's entrustment and embarked on the journey of looking for 30 companions with different personalities to attack the Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/4079bc3aeba1b8517687cd28a6dce10a.avif?t=1772420076\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Japanese SRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 characters to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich story</p></li></ul>",
